text: We had a BBQ party on last Saturday at East Coast park, taht was excited moment for all our HDEC family.
It is a very peaceful place, you can feel relaxed with the nature
Nice park, good for jogging and cycling
Cycled past here many times, quite quiet as it's the "ulu" end of ECP. You'll surely pass by here if you want to head to TMCR, NSRCC or that dinosaur area at the airport
